## Best Practices for High-Impact CTWA Campaigns

To succeed, you need more than just setting up the ad. Here is how to maximize your overall return:

🟢 **Use a Clear Call-to-Action**
Your ad copy should be exceptionally clear. Tell users exactly what happens next. Examples: "Chat with an expert," "Get your personalized quote on WhatsApp," or "Claim your discount via chat."

🟢 **Automate Your First Response**
Never make a Click-to-WhatsApp user wait. Integrate an AI agent to welcome them instantly, collect their initial details, and route them effectively before they switch apps.

🟢 **Offer Value in Exchange for the Chat**
People are fiercely protective of their inbox. Offer immediate value—like a custom PDF, early access codes, or a diagnostic quiz—as the starting point of the conversation.

🟢 **Review and Optimize with CAPI Data**
Keep a close eye on your Conversions API dashboards. Look at which ad variations and audiences are driving the highest quality conversations, rather than simply measuring the lowest cost-per-click.

