## Frequently Asked Questions

**What are Click to WhatsApp Ads?**
They are targeted advertisements on Facebook and Instagram that open a direct WhatsApp chat window with your business instead of taking the user to a standard website or landing page.

**What is CAPI and why is it important for WhatsApp ads?**
CAPI stands for Conversions API. It allows your system to send downstream conversion data (like purchases or subscriptions) securely back to Meta. This trains the Meta ad algorithm to find better, higher-intent customers instead of just generating superficial clicks.

**How does ChatzyAI improve WhatsApp ad campaigns?**
ChatzyAI automates immediate and intelligent responses to incoming ad traffic so users are never left waiting. Furthermore, with its built-in CAPI integration, ChatzyAI tracks high-value actions in the chat and feeds this data back to Meta to automatically optimize your ad delivery.

**Do I need a WhatsApp Business account?**
Yes. To run Click-to-WhatsApp ads and integrate with advanced AI routing platforms like ChatzyAI, you need a WhatsApp Business profile connected to the official WhatsApp Business API.

**Is it expensive to respond to CTWA leads?**
Meta provides a 72-hour Free Entry Point (FEP) window when a user initiates a conversation from a Click-to-WhatsApp ad. This means you have 72 hours of extensive organic messaging with the lead without incurring extra template message costs.

